sequenceDiagram
    participant EUUser
    participant EUWallet
    participant eIDAS
    participant ServiceProvider
    participant PublicAdmin
    participant CrossBorderSystem

    Note over EUUser,CrossBorderSystem: Scenario: EU citizen/business uses Digital Identity Wallet.
    EUUser->>EUWallet: Log In
    EUWallet->>eIDAS: Verify Identity (e.g., via national eID)
    eIDAS-->>EUWallet: Identity Verification Result
    EUUser->>EUWallet: Request Service Access
    EUWallet->>ServiceProvider: Grant Access (e.g., to Banks/Public Services)
    EUUser->>EUWallet: Store & Share Credentials
    EUWallet->>VerifiedStorage: Store Verified Credentials
    PublicAdmin->>EUWallet: Request Identity Validation
    EUWallet-->>PublicAdmin: Validate Identity (e.g., for permits)
    CrossBorderSystem->>EUWallet: Request Interoperability Check
    EUWallet-->>CrossBorderSystem: Confirm Interoperability (e.g., across member states)
